{
  "texts": [
    "Personalization in further avenues could better improve the clinical outcomes of ART.",
    "Ovarian response has been shown to vary significantly depending on ovarian reserve, between ethnic groups 114, 115, FSH receptor genetic polymorphisms 116, and body weight 19, 117.",
    "Therefore, incorporating such factors which influence pharmacokinetic parameters when dosing gonadotropins 9, 19, 20, or suppressing premature ovulation 20, 118, may be beneficial.",
    "ML methods could also help tailor luteal phase support regimens to certain patient subgroups, where a lack of clinical consensus currently exists 119.",
    "The ubiquity of electronic health records (EHRs) has accelerated the development of CDSSs 15."
  ]
}